# Client-side
<client>
<features>
NTLM
SSL
!SSPI
Debug
</features>
<server>
http
</server>
<name>
HTTP POST with NTLM authorization and following a 302 redirect
</name>
<command>
http://%HOSTIP:%HTTPPORT/%TESTNUMBER -u testuser:testpass --ntlm -L -d "stuff to send away"
</command>
</client>

